
1. All links in the text should be highlighted.

It is possible to use an application of different colors, italics or bold.

2. Lines must be separated by spaces for readability.

Ideally, the distance between lines should be made about one and a half times larger than the size of the font used for typing.

3. Do not use small font size.

If the font size is less than twelve pixels, the readability of the text is severely affected.

4. The texts of the site have to be illustrated by thematic pictures.
Of course, the pictures should correspond to the text of the articles.

5. It is necessary to follow the optimal length of the lines.

The size of the string should be less than hundred characters. Otherwise it can negatively affect the readability.
